<ptxt>Disconnect the negative (-) terminal cable from the battery, and wait for at least 90 seconds.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Replace the occupant classification ECU (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM0000011JG003X"/>).</ptxt>
<atten4>
<ptxt>Perform the inspection using parts from a normal vehicle if possible.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM0000010VF00NX_04_0025" fin="false">NEXT</down>
</res>
</testgrp>
